{"tid":154216,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"容永棋：有需要讓年輕人深入理解「一國兩制」","createTime":"2017-03-13T06:46:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-13T11:04:34.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c20b83060ea74160b8d2dae10bd998ae22a7a9a7","tid":154216,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T06:46:09.000Z","msg":"全國政協第十二屆第五次會議早上在北京閉幕，獲通過的政協常委會工作報告中，有關港澳部份，加入了堅持反對「港獨」行徑，以及助推港區政協委員走進校園展開國情教育活動等的新內容。<br />\n<br />\n政協委員容永棋認為，香港是國家的一部份，香港已回歸20周年，有需要讓年輕人深入理解「一國兩制」，了解國家過去與現在和發展，加強對國家認識。<br />\n<br />\n另一名政協譚耀宗亦認為，到學校向學生和家長介紹《基本法》的起草情況，讓青年人了解和知道更多，可以減少誤解。"},{"pid":"5113defc0a6114276b07ff31753f98366d9f8002","tid":154216,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T06:46:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1318829-20170313.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1318829-20170313.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Fy0o8YzXie14Yexn7W6rufjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=83a19c8c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1318829-20170313.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=bd88968d\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1318829-20170313.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"f1bd7243c76a599f31732abd3938263953177568","tid":154216,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T06:59:06.000Z","msg":"就係了解完先知真相"},{"pid":"bc0e6059cc3bc4a0d3b765bd9940213f3afdfa92","tid":154216,"uid":3007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T07:01:36.000Z","msg":"明明就係成班垃圾唔理解<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3a74576739ab95b6caffc36949ae03ce2d0cbf1","tid":154216,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T07:05:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14d46eaa9c400a1c